00:34:24.270 --> 00:34:25.271
Eu te sperii?

00:34:25.354 --> 00:34:27.482
Rău de tot. Da, absolut.

00:34:29.692 --> 00:34:30.651
Bun, ce fa…

00:34:34.155 --> 00:34:35.615
Ești speriată, Miller?

00:34:37.241 --> 00:34:38.451
