00:35:23.788 --> 00:35:24.956
Nu te susțin?

00:35:56.154 --> 00:35:57.989
Ginny Miller. Abby Littman.

00:35:58.072 --> 00:35:59.448
Tocmai chiuleați?

00:36:00.908 --> 00:36:01.784
Hai cu mine!

00:36:11.085 --> 00:36:12.003
Alo!

00:36:12.795 --> 00:36:13.796
